description:
As Princess Cadences heart shatters, the world begins to wither, plunging everything into despair. In a desperate final battle against Queen Chrysalis, Cadence must overcome her heartbreak and reignite the power of love before the world succumbs to darkness forever. 
Will her shattered heart doom Equestria, or can she prove that loves light can outshine even the deepest despair?
Featuring this beautiful rendition of This Day Aria!! by https://x.com/rakuda_ch
https://youtu.be/Rp6yqNG60_0
